Package: FusioMR
Type: Package
Title: Fusion Mendelian Randomization Framework
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given  = "Sihao",
           family = "Feng",
           email  = "sfeng56@uchicago.edu",
           role   = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements a flexible, unified, and versatile framework for 
    Mendelian Randomization analysis using Bayesian approaches with Gibbs sampling. 
    Provides functions for instrumental variable selection with provided p_value 
    and causal effect estimation from GWAS summary statistics.
